trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> is used in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> to maintain a list of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> objects to match.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> é usado em uma <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> para manter uma lista de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> objetos para corresponder.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: O construtor padrão inicializa o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> para uma lista vazia.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection" /> class by using a list of workflow track points.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection" /> usando uma lista de pontos de acompanhamento de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> objects specified in `points`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> é inicializada para conter o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> objetos especificados em `points`.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="points" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="points" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).
